Diglett (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0049: Venomoth
Pokémon
#0051: Dugtrio →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Diglett (TCG Pocket).

Diglett has been featured on 26 different cards since it debuted in the Base Set of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Diglett cards are normally Fighting-type or Metal-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Diglett

Diglett
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
